Maintainer: Maximilian Scholz <research.scholz@mailbox.org>
Description: A comprehensive simulation framework for Bayesian modeling studies.
    Provides tools for running complex simulation studies with brms models,
    including parallel processing, comprehensive metrics calculation, and
    advanced analyses like Simulation-Based Calibration (SBC). Supports
    custom data generation processes and extensible metric systems.
